    "description": "# Order Management System API\n\nThis Postman collection contains all APIs required for the Order Management System assignment.\n\n## Features\n\n- Create Order\n    \n- Get All Orders\n    \n- Filter Orders by Status\n    \n- Run Scheduler\n    \n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- baseURL\n    \n- scheduler_secret\n    \n\n## Scheduler\n\nThe scheduler endpoint is protected using the `x-secret-key` header and is automatically triggered in production using GitHub Actions.",
